data.description: This beautifully well maintained property is an absolute must see. This gorgeous home boasts everything from a 3 car garage to a massive basement. The living room has beautiful built-in's, the shower's have custom tile, the master walk-in closet has so much room. Don't miss the beautiful granite counter tops and large walk-in pantry in the kitchen. The a/c and furnace were just recently replaced. The huge 1,100 sqft basement offers a kitchen, bedroom, full rec room and has the potential for a mother-inlaw quarters or a large second living space. This property is on one of the largest lots in Legacy Woods and has a massive fenced in back yard that has endless potential for a back yard oasis or large entertainment space. Don't miss out on having such a gorgeous property that is just minutes from just about anywhere in the city.
